        "pattern": "Historical Reclamation",
        "explanation": "Breaking rules evokes earlier musical eras",
        "example": "Parallel 5ths evoke medieval organum; polytonality evokes pre-tonal chaos"
      },
      {
        "pattern": "Emotional Authenticity",
        "explanation": "Ambiguity and non-resolution better express complex emotional states than clean resolution",
        "example": "Radiohead's floating tonic creates unresolved emotional state"
      },
      {
        "pattern": "Timbral Considerations",
